com.inqwell.any.jms

Interface SessionI

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Any, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AnySession

    public interface SessionI
extends Any
    Access to a JMS Session within the Any framework.

    Not all the underlying interface methods (on JMS Connection) are replicated here, only the ones we (intend to) use.

    Author:
    tom
